  "detailed_description": "Step into the mind of Mike and explore the depths of a twisted reality in this heart-pounding psychological horror first-person platformer. Dodge deadly obstacles at every turn and unravel the truth hidden deep within Mike's psych as you navigate his tormented memories.<br><br><strong>But beware; she is watching your every move.</strong> <br><br>Can you solve the puzzles and escape this nightmarish world before its too late?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658180/extras/bc36d60d60f1bd42027bd29be2f48a24.poster.avif?t=1743190384\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658180/extras/bc36d60d60f1bd42027bd29be2f48a24.webm?t=1743190384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658180/extras/bc36d60d60f1bd42027bd29be2f48a24.mp4?t=1743190384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br><strong>Solve Puzzles</strong><br><br>Master the nightmarish world within Mike's mind and, solve puzzles as you work your way back to reality. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658180/extras/85e2eb59c14954c3e2027747693059f0.poster.avif?t=1743190384\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658180/extras/85e2eb59c14954c3e2027747693059f0.webm?t=1743190384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658180/extras/85e2eb59c14954c3e2027747693059f0.mp4?t=1743190384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br><br><br><strong>Dodge deadly obstacles</strong><br><br>Plan each move carefully; and avoid deadly obstacles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658180/extras/6f6ed9ec9491b1cb13345487bd3b5a89.poster.avif?t=1743190384\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658180/extras/6f6ed9ec9491b1cb13345487bd3b5a89.webm?t=1743190384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658180/extras/6f6ed9ec9491b1cb13345487bd3b5a89.mp4?t=1743190384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br><br><strong>Key features:</strong><br><br><strong>Psychological Puzzle Solving:</strong> Delve into the depths of Mike's mind as you solve intricate puzzles and unravel the mysteries of his suppressed memories.<br><br><strong>Immersive Atmospheric Experience:</strong> Immerse yourself in a hauntingly atmospheric world, where every shadow and sound contribute to the suspenseful and emotional journey.<br><strong><br>Precision Dodging:</strong> Master the art of precision dodging as you narrowly escape the razor-sharp edges of deadly saws. Each movement counts, making every evasion a pulse-pounding moment of skill and strategy.<br><br><strong>Sinister Narration:</strong> Experience an unsettling narrative as the tormenting voice narrates Mike's journey, injecting a sinister tone into every revelation and decision, creating an immersive and eerie storytelling experience.<br><br><strong>Do you have what it takes to escape the unknown?</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "Step into the mind of Mike and explore the depths of a twisted reality in this heart-pounding psychological horror first-person platformer. Dodge deadly obstacles at every turn and unravel the truth hidden deep within Mike's psych as you navigate his tormented memories.<br><br><strong>But beware; she is watching your every move.</strong> <br><br>Can you solve the puzzles and escape this nightmarish world before its too late?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658180/extras/bc36d60d60f1bd42027bd29be2f48a24.poster.avif?t=1743190384\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658180/extras/bc36d60d60f1bd42027bd29be2f48a24.webm?t=1743190384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658180/extras/bc36d60d60f1bd42027bd29be2f48a24.mp4?t=1743190384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br><strong>Solve Puzzles</strong><br><br>Master the nightmarish world within Mike's mind and, solve puzzles as you work your way back to reality. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658180/extras/85e2eb59c14954c3e2027747693059f0.poster.avif?t=1743190384\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658180/extras/85e2eb59c14954c3e2027747693059f0.webm?t=1743190384\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658180/extras/85e2eb59c14954c3e2027747693059f0.mp4?t=1743190384\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>.<br><br><br><br><strong>Dodge deadly obstacles</strong><br><br>Plan each move carefully; and avoid deadly obstacles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><